description: Returns a paginated list of DataIntegration associations in the account.

parameters.name: DataIntegrationIdentifier
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the DataIntegration.

nested_items.name: DataIntegrationAssociations
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) and unique ID of the DataIntegration association.

nested_items.name: DataIntegrationAssociationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the DataIntegration association.

nested_items.name: DataIntegrationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the DataIntegration.

nested_items.name: ClientId
nested_items.description: The identifier for the client that is associated with the DataIntegration association.

nested_items.name: DestinationURI
nested_items.description: The URI of the data destination.

nested_items.name: LastExecutionStatus
nested_items.description: The execution status of the last job.

nested_items.name: StatusMessage
nested_items.description: The status message of a job.

nested_items.name: ExecutionConfiguration
nested_items.description: The configuration for how the files should be pulled from the source.

nested_items.name: ExecutionMode
nested_items.description: The mode for data import/export execution.

nested_items.name: OnDemandConfiguration
nested_items.description: The start and end time for data pull from the source.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The start time for data pull from the source as an Unix/epoch string in milliseconds.

nested_items.name: EndTime
nested_items.description: The end time for data pull from the source as an Unix/epoch string in milliseconds.

nested_items.name: ScheduleConfiguration
nested_items.description: The name of the data and how often it should be pulled from the source.

nested_items.name: FirstExecutionFrom
nested_items.description: The start date for objects to import in the first flow run as an Unix/epoch timestamp in milliseconds or in ISO-8601 format.

nested_items.name: Object
nested_items.description: The name of the object to pull from the data source.

nested_items.name: ScheduleExpression
nested_items.description: How often the data should be pulled from data source.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If there are additional results, this is the token for the next set of results.
